Characters
Haruto Kirishima
Haruto is a high-school pupil Hiroshima, in Sh?bara. He chastises the others when they have been in the incorrect and has a serious disposition. Haruto considers it as an profession and is proficient at cooking, because he regularly cooks for his relatives and buddies. His older sister Aoi[Jp 1]Ch. 19 lives in Tokyo in the dorm-room next to the Akitsukis from Suzuka.Station. 80 He has a longtime crush on classmate Nanami Kanzaki, but his emotions change towards Yuzuki as the show advances. By the end of the show, he weds Yuzuki, has a son named Daiki, and opens up his own eatery.Ch. 261 In equally Tatsunko Production's as well as Gonzo's japanimation, he's expressed by Yoshimasa Hosoya.
